The paper discusses question answering, which is a topic that falls under several sub-categories of computer science. Specifically, the paper focuses on creating question answering datasets and competitions, which involves natural language processing (cs.CL), machine learning (cs.AI, cs.LG), information retrieval (cs.IR), and human-computer interaction (cs.HC). Therefore, these five sub-categories are the most likely candidates for this paper.
